      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/ba8739/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2024-06-04T09:36:47.138Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hello,<br>\nThis issue is caused by the fact our SSL provider stopped supporting Android 7, that\u2019s why you are not able to access any site that use Letsencrypt and probably many other ssl certifications.<br>\nHere\u2019s the official list of Certificate Compatibility:</p><aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <a href=\"https://letsencrypt.org/docs/certificate-compatibility/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">letsencrypt.org</a>\n  </header>\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:690/362;\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/c0f71b11acf471cb0064575038886ed2fcc9a16b_2_690x362.png\" class=\"thumbnail\" width=\"690\" height=\"362\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/c0f71b11acf471cb0064575038886ed2fcc9a16b_2_690x362.png, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/c0f71b11acf471cb0064575038886ed2fcc9a16b_2_1035x543.png 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/c/c0f71b11acf471cb0064575038886ed2fcc9a16b.png 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/c0f71b11acf471cb0064575038886ed2fcc9a16b_2_10x10.png\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://letsencrypt.org/docs/certificate-compatibility/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Certificate Compatibility -  Let's Encrypt</a></h3>\n\n<p>The determining factor for whether a platform can validate Let\u2019s Encrypt certificates is whether that platform trusts ISRG\u2019s \u201cISRG Root X1\u201d or \u201cISRG Root X2\u201d certificates. Both of these roots have been included in...</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n<p>Br,<br>\nMarek</p>",
